        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and used divination and enchantments: to get knowledge of what was to be done at present, or of things to come, neglecting the word of God and his prophets, and acting against the express law of God, Deuteronomy 18:10. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and used divination and enchantments: to get knowledge of what was to be done at present, or of things to come, neglecting the word of God and his prophets, and acting against the express law of God, ",
