      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "used divination and enchantments",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] The former word probably refers to some way of seeking out guidance by lots, or by arrows with different marks on them, and the words on the selected one were taken as a direction what to do (cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
