        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). The latter word refers to omens derived from sights or sounds. This was the way in which Joseph used his divining cup (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Genesis 44:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
